{"tid":1232683,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好衝！！！！","createTime":"2019-06-16T16:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T00:19:39.000Z","uid":187640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7df427f0930bbf2c30e8086afaa9b2c46ba27149","tid":1232683,"uid":187640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"大家今晚千其唔好衝！唔好比犬有藉口用更強武力。<br />\n記住，留既去宗教集會唱聖詩，見有人搗亂即刻制止！（佢地可能係鬼）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5006388090dd2e8c0fbdb82d5c6414f2a5b222ad","tid":1232683,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:12:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中報導一事，已經嚴重違反電視通用業務守則中有關「第9章準確、持平及公正」，當中要求「持牌人必須盡一切合理努力，確保新聞、時事節目...的真實資料準確無誤」，以及「持牌人必須確保新聞節目...能夠恰當地持平」，「不可使用謬誤資料或歪曲事實。持牌人亦不應錯誤引導觀眾，以致對節目提及的人士或團體不公平」<br />\n<br />\nTVB在反送中的報導完全扭曲事相，報導嚴重偏袒警方和政府，報導失實 ， 偏頗，例如6月12日的「六點半新聞報道」和「晚間新聞」，完全不播放及不提及：<br />\n1. 警方違法向多名記者開槍，棍打記者<br />\n2. 警方違法瞄準市民頭部發射布袋彈和橡膠子彈<br />\n3. 在沒有任何襲擊下，警方違法向婦孺、伯伯開槍<br />\n4. 警方違法向市民投擲鐵枝、磗頭<br />\n5. 隻字不提一些市民向警方掟水樽垃圾等之前，警方在多處在沒有受到任何襲擊，提出任何警告下，違法突然向市民開槍，不斷發射催淚彈，布袋彈和橡膠子彈，導致局勢快速失控<br />\n6.隻字不提有市民於6月15日於太古廣場因展示示威標語墮樓, 送院搶救後不治的事實<br />\n<br />\n投訴表格：<a href=\"https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.coms-auth.hk%2Fapps%2Fbroadcasting_complaint%2Findex.aspx%3Flang%3D2&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=5fc3e25e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apps.coms-auth.hk/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span>"},{"pid":"1ae8e3ac822be0297ac0be063b63cf4cb679bb38","tid":1232683,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7df427f0930bbf2c30e8086afaa9b2c46ba27149","tid":1232683,"uid":187640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"大家今晚千其唔好衝！唔好比犬有藉口用更強武力。<br />\n記住，留既去宗教集會唱聖詩，見有人搗亂即刻制止！（佢地可能係鬼）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:12:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"759579dabefb248fb5cb56503cada60d38b23963","tid":1232683,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7df427f0930bbf2c30e8086afaa9b2c46ba27149","tid":1232683,"uid":187640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"大家今晚千其唔好衝！唔好比犬有藉口用更強武力。<br />\n記住，留既去宗教集會唱聖詩，見有人搗亂即刻制止！（佢地可能係鬼）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T00:16:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f211e4e341e0852446fd5b1d762a3812a95c435","tid":1232683,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7df427f0930bbf2c30e8086afaa9b2c46ba27149","tid":1232683,"uid":187640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"大家今晚千其唔好衝！唔好比犬有藉口用更強武力。<br />\n記住，留既去宗教集會唱聖詩，見有人搗亂即刻制止！（佢地可能係鬼）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj